dct_title_s: Kilimanjaro : Tanzania 1:100 000 / Kartenwerk der Arbeitsgemeinschaft für Vergleichende Hochgebirgsforschung e.V.; cartographic work: Ethan Oleson ; project management: Andreas Hemp, Bayreuth, Manfred F. Buchroithner.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, shading,  spot heights, and rock drawings. Map shows international boundaries, vegetation distribution, land-use, potable water sources, camp-sites, roads, railroads, major power lines, points of interest. Arc 1960, U.T.M. Zone field 37M. Includes location map. This map is a source for data analysis on the effects of climate and land-use on biodiversity and the ecosystem.
dct_publisher_sm: Munich : Arbeitsgemeinschaft für Vergleichende Hochgebirgsforschung e.V.
